<br>
SK and Pal want to tank as well as me? They aren't far off already.  They are the clear choice in xp groups and are close to being MT for raids on most big mobs.  Shield buffs will only make them more efficient at tanking - maybe warriors will be <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  slightly</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> ahead still, but we give up taunt to them.  It would most likely be better for the raid to spend a bit more mana healing the Pal/SK and not have other classes worrying about over-agroing - hence killing the mob faster anyway.<br>
<br>
You want to tank as well as me and do as much damage as me? Fine, give us all your spells.<br>
<br>
The only solutions I could see at the moment, is put us on a slightly better defensive table, maybe 5% better. If the shield fix goes live, allow us to block with offhand weapons.  Give us abilities similar in use to monk flying kick etc.  Some that do an extra couple of hundred damage every 10-15 seconds, some that give us  taunt etc.  Have them scale with levels like the monk skills do.<br>
<br>
That would fix warriors at all levels without having us rely on items.<br>
<br>
My 2cp.<br>
