A maximum of 3 levels difference will exist over 60 levels. That would indicate that no matter what race or class you play there is a maximum of 5% difference in experience over 60 levels between any race or class. Now...if you take into account the racial penalty for large races, and the racial bonus for small races, then that doesn't leave a helluva lot of bonus to experience by being a warrior instead of a hybrid.<br>
<br>
I looked through all the patch messages on that board and couldn't even find the one that changed the damage tables, let alone the one I remember talking about experience bonuses. Unfortunately, the patch message archive only goes back a couple of months, and the developer's corner didn't detail all the patches, but I think this quote puts to rest this malarky about a 10% bonus to warrior's experience. <br>
